    "Details": "The E configuration, introduced in 3063 by Clan Star Adder, centers on an ATM 6 launcher in the right arm fed by one ton each of Extended-Range and High-Explosive ammunition, giving the pilot engagement flexibility across multiple range bands. A Heavy Medium Laser in the left arm provides substantial close-range damage, backed by a head-mounted Heavy Small Laser. Heat management demands careful attention during sustained close-range combat.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Improved Communications</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.98</color></b>",
